sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant DA as create_deep_agent
    participant MW as Middleware Stack
    participant M as Model (Claude)
    participant T as Tool
    participant BE as Backend
    U->>DA: invoke({messages: [...]})
    DA->>MW: before_agent hooks
    MW->>MW: MemoryMiddleware loads AGENTS.md
    MW->>MW: SkillsMiddleware loads SKILL.md metadata
    loop until no tool calls
        MW->>M: wrap_model_call
        M-->>MW: assistant + toolCall
        MW->>T: wrap_tool_call
        T->>BE: state update via Command
        T-->>MW: ToolMessage
    end
    MW-->>U: final state (messages + files + todos)
